Scalars.Comment: IIAA = Inschrijving In de Administratie van de Aangever
Scalars.ExtendedAttributesText:
{1626A879-DBAC-4E54-8A36-28FCB761FF3A},MDDE_LDM,479={38253E88-8698-4A5B-8398-0FA2B14556C0},mdde_SqlExpression,415=@EndAsAttr = CASE WHEN LEFT(@ProcedureCategory,1)  = 'I'  THEN 'IIAA'
                  WHEN @AdittionalDeclarationType  = 'Z'  THEN 'IIAA'
                  WHEN LEFT(@ProcedureCategory,1)  = 'B'  THEN 'Export'
                  WHEN @ProcedureCategory          = 'H2' THEN 'Opslag'
                  WHEN LEFT(@ProcedureCategory,1)  = 'H'  THEN 'Import'
                  ELSE 'Onbekend'
             END
